Subject: [PATCH V8 04/16] rv/include: Add deterministic automata monitor definition via C macros
Date:   Wed, 27 Jul 2022 19:11:32 +0200
Message-Id: <5a872ddcb2cdbe4ae17f1c45f71ca6cbfa688f26.1658940828.git.bristot@kernel.org>
